      <trans-unit id="3238381523520662024" datatype="html">
        <source> My name is <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>Krishna Kumar Pandey<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/>. I currently work as a <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>Technical Assistant<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> at the <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bengaluru<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/>. Most days involve a quiet balance of <x id="START_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;em&gt;"/>web development<x id="CLOSE_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;/em&gt;"/>, <x id="START_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;em&gt;"/>systems support<x id="CLOSE_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;/em&gt;"/>, and ensuring that research and operations keep moving without friction. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/about/about.component.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">18,23</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="1023368672790575603" datatype="html">
        <source> I completed my <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>MCA<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> from <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>JAIN (Deemed-to-be University)<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> and my <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>BCA<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/> from <x id="START_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;strong&gt;"/>Acharya Institute of Graduate Studies<x id="CLOSE_TAG_STRONG" ctype="x-strong" equiv-text="&lt;/strong&gt;"/>. Through these years, I was fortunate to be recognised for academic and extracurricular excellence, but it was the habit of <x id="START_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;em&gt;"/>writing, coding, and staying curious<x id="CLOSE_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;/em&gt;"/> that stuck with me most. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/about/about.component.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">24,29</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="7525184255346123173" datatype="html">
        <source> My technical work ranges from developing academic portals and dashboards to building custom tools using Angular and the MERN stack. I’ve also contributed to automation workflows and server-side scripting for smoother research operations. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/about/about.component.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">30,31</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="3883967780100902154" datatype="html">
        <source> Outside of code, I enjoy mentoring, editing, and collaborating on creative projects. Whether it’s preparing students for exams or helping a team shape their ideas — I find purpose in clear communication and thoughtful execution. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/about/about.component.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">35,36</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
