      <trans-unit id="8771016874269577874" datatype="html">
        <source> This is where I share thoughts on <x id="START_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;em&gt;"/>technology<x id="CLOSE_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;/em&gt;"/>, <x id="START_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;em&gt;"/>competitive exams<x id="CLOSE_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;/em&gt;"/>, and <x id="START_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;em&gt;"/>life lessons<x id="CLOSE_EMPHASISED_TEXT" ctype="x-em" equiv-text="&lt;/em&gt;"/> — experiences shaped through learning, writing, and working in the field. </source>
