      <trans-unit id="2282121692318423774" datatype="html">
        <source> The journey so far has brought me to the Indian Institute of Science (IISc), Bengaluru, where I serve as a Technical Assistant. My work spans systems, development, and support — often blending code with curiosity. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/home/home.component.html</context>
          <context context-type="linenumber">10,11</context>
        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="422465141051351389" datatype="html">
        <source> Along the way, I completed my MCA from JAIN University, cleared GATE and NET, and built tools with Angular and the MERN stack. This space continues that journey — one post at a time. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
          <context context-type="sourcefile">src/app/pages/home/home.component.html</context>
