        </context-group>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="4612759765845907741" datatype="html">
        <source> Here are some of the tools, dashboards, and applications I&apos;ve built over the years — academic, personal, and exploratory. </source>
        <context-group purpose="location">
